---
/**
 * Lifestyle — editorial two-column section.
 * Large image left with numbered caption, copy block right.
 */
---

<section class="lifestyle" data-reveal>
  <p class="lifestyle__label">The Lifestyle</p>

  <div class="lifestyle__grid">
    <div class="lifestyle__media">
      <div class="lifestyle__image">
        <img src="/images/lifestyle-neighbourhood.jpg" alt="Couple walking along the bay at golden hour, Edgewater neighbourhood" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="lifestyle__caption">
        <p class="lifestyle__caption-number">(6)</p>
        <p class="lifestyle__caption-text">Designed around the hours you actually keep</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lifestyle__copy">
      <p>
        A cold plunge before sunrise. Laps in the infinity pool while the bay
        turns from silver to blue. Yoga on the terrace with nothing but
        horizon in front of you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every amenity is designed around the hours you actually keep. Early
        mornings that start quietly, long evenings that don't need to go
        anywhere. The wellness floor, the resident lounge, the landscaped
        podium. None of it performs. It just works.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lifestyle__pair">
    <div class="lifestyle__pair-image">
      <img src="/images/lifestyle-yoga.jpg" alt="Morning yoga on a wooden terrace, aerial view" loading="lazy" data-parallax />
    </div>
    <div class="lifestyle__pair-image">
      <img src="/images/lifestyle-plunge.jpg" alt="Cold plunge pool in warm ambient light" loading="lazy" data-parallax />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
